he presence of both supports. The relative concentration of these\nspecies was lower in the case of the porous \\ce{SiO2} beads for all applied\nvoltages, which suggests that surface reactions are more significant than gas\nphase reactions for the formation of \\ce{NH3} in plasma assisted \\ce{NH3}\nsynthesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Nov 2021 21:19:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-09"}
